== 负面事件 ==
=== 駭客入侵 ===
2011年4月17-19日，PSN受到駭客攻击，迫使索尼于4月20日暂停服务，中断长达23天，影响到7700万注册用户<ref>{{Cite web|title=PlayStation Network and Qriocity Outage FAQ|url=https://blog.eu.playstation.com/2011/04/28/playstation-network-and-qriocity-outage-faq/|work=PlayStation.Blog.Europe|date=2011-04-28|accessdate=2019-02-28|language=en|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228192517/https://blog.eu.playstation.com/2011/04/28/playstation-network-and-qriocity-outage-faq/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后索尼公布发现有用户数据遭到泄露<ref>{{Cite web|title=Update on PlayStation Network and Qriocity|url=https://blog.us.playstation.com/2011/04/26/update-on-playstation-network-and-qriocity/|work=PlayStation.Blog|accessdate=2019-02-28|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228192454/https://blog.us.playstation.com/2011/04/26/update-on-playstation-network-and-qriocity/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年6月，索尼在恢复服务后推出「欢迎回来」（Welcome Back）补偿计划，允许在4月20日之前注册的用户免费下载PS3和PSP游戏各两个，以及30天的免费PS Plus订阅，服务中断前已订阅的用户则获得60天<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sony launches 'Welcome Back' program for PSN users|url=http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/06/sony-launches-welcome-back-program-for-psn-users/1|work=今日美国|accessdate=2019-02-28|archive-date=2011-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605025756/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/06/sony-launches-welcome-back-program-for-psn-users/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
=== 受DDoS攻击 ===
2014年12月25日，PSN与[[Xbox_Live|Xbox Live]]同时受到大量[[拒绝服务攻击|DDoS攻击]]导致服务暂时中断，于26日恢复<ref>{{Cite web|title=Playstation Network and Xbox Live Down Since Christmas|url=https://thenextweb.com/insider/2014/12/26/playstation-network-xbox-live-since-christmas/|work=The Next Web|date=2014-12-26|accessdate=2019-02-28|language=en-us|first=Abhimanyu|last=Ghoshal|archive-date=2020-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801224304/https://thenextweb.com/insider/2014/12/26/playstation-network-xbox-live-since-christmas/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年1月1日，索尼宣布补偿用户5天免费PS Plus订阅<ref>{{Cite web|title=Sony Rewards PSN Users' Patience With Free Five Day Extension|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2015/01/01/sony-rewards-psn-users-patience-with-free-five-day-extentsion|work=IGN|date=2015-01-01|accessdate=2019-02-28|language=en-US|first=Michael|last=Martin|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228192501/https://www.ign.com/articles/2015/01/01/sony-rewards-psn-users-patience-with-free-five-day-extentsion|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

